<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SiRajin - Error <%= error.status || 500 %></title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .error-container {
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='100' height='100' viewBox='0 0 100 100' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M11 18c3.866 0 7-3.134 7-7s-3.134-7-7-7-7 3.134-7 7 3.134 7 7 7zm48 25c3.866 0 7-3.134 7-7s-3.134-7-7-7-7 3.134-7 7 3.134 7 7 7zm-43-7c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zm63 31c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zM34 90c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zm56-76c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zM12 86c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm28-65c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm23-11c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zm-6 60c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm29 22c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zM32 63c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zm57-13c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zm-9-21c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2zM60 91c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2zM35 41c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2zM12 60c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2z' fill='%230ea5e9' fill-opacity='0.05' fill-rule='evenodd'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-md w-full space-y-8 p-10 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg error-container">
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="flex justify-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-16 w-16 text-red-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="mt-6 text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">
                    Error <%= error.status || 500 %>
                </h2>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Maaf, terjadi kesalahan saat memproses permintaan Anda.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-4 rounded">
                <div class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ml-3">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-red-800">
                            <%= error.name || 'Server Error' %>
                        </h3>
                        <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-red-700">
                            <p><%= error.message %></p>
                            <% if (error.stack && process.env.NODE_ENV !== 'production') { %>
                                <details class="mt-3">
                                    <summary class="text-sm cursor-pointer text-red-600">Stack trace</summary>
                                    <pre class="mt-2 p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded overflow-x-auto text-xs text-gray-800"><%= error.stack %></pre>
                                </details>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6">
                <div class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
                    <p>Silakan coba lagi atau hubungi tim dukungan kami jika masalah berlanjut.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                    <a href="/" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700">
                        Kembali ke Beranda
                    </a>
                    <a href="mailto:support@sirajin.com" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-primary-700 bg-primary-100 hover:bg-primary-200">
                        Hubungi Dukungan
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <% if (process.env.NODE_ENV !== 'production' && error.details) { %>
                <div class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-200 pt-6">
                    <h4 class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Debug Details</h4>
                    <pre class="mt-2 p-3 bg-gray-100 rounded overflow-x-auto text-xs text-gray-800"><%= JSON.stringify(error.details, null, 2) %></pre>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>